org.itsnat.comp.list

Interface ItsNatHTMLSelectMult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ItsNatComponent, ItsNatElementComponent, ItsNatHTMLElementComponent, ItsNatHTMLFormComponent, ItsNatHTMLSelect, ItsNatList, ItsNatListMultSel, ItsNatUserData

    public interface ItsNatHTMLSelectMult
extends ItsNatHTMLSelect, ItsNatListMultSel
    Is the interface of multiple selection list components based on HTML select elements.

    ItsNat provides a default implementation of this interface.

    Author:
    Jose Maria Arranz Santamaria
